ANCRegistry 0..*BaseANC - RMNCAH - Antenatal care registry (ANC)
ancUid 0..1stringUnique Identifier for ANC record
ancEtMrn 1..1stringClient MRN
grandfathersName 1..1stringGrandfather's Name (in the case of other countries, Family name or last name of the patient of case.)
firstName 1..1stringFirst Name (in other countries, this may be Given Name)
ageDateOfBirth 0..1AgeAge/Date of birth
ageYears 0..1unsignedIntAge in years
faydaNationalAliasNumber 0..1stringFayda National Alias Number (FAN/FCN)
mobileNumber 0..1stringClient's mobile phone number
occupation 0..1codeANC.B6. Occupation
Binding: Occupation value set (required)
educationLevel 0..1codeEducation level
Binding: ANC.B6. Education level value set (required)
specifyOtherEducationLevel 0..1stringSpecify other education level
maritalStatus 0..1codeMarital Status
Binding: Marital Status value set (required)
addressDistrict 0..1stringDistrict of current address of the patient or case.
addressParish 0..1stringKebele of current address of the patient
addressVillage 0..1stringVillage of current address of the patient
fathersName 0..1stringFather's name (in other countries, this may also refer to a woman's Maiden Names)
otherNames 0..1stringOther names
smsMobileNumber 0..1stringClient's SMS mobile phone number
womansProfileAndHistory 0..1WomansProfileAndHistoryWoman's Profile and History
ancExamination 0..*ANCExaminationANC Examination
laboratoryTestsAndImaging 0..*LaboratoryTestsAndImagingInformation regarding various laboratory tests and imaging conducted for diagnostic and curative services the current pregnancy
promotionAndTreatment 0..*PromotionAndTreatmentData elements for the counselling and treatment task of the workflow
pregnancyOutcome 0..*PregnancyOutcomePregnancy outcome
postpartum 0..*PostpartumPostpartum
